{"tid":1573560,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際文宣戰鄭重建議】+ 【抵制TVB】每日洗版任務 (樂信)","createTime":"2019-09-16T04:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T01:13:15.000Z","uid":267969,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d08bd6fb9343f5ff12e430863c63f2b7bcf8f764","tid":1573560,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為P牌，所以兩段文字一齊開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#1 【國際文宣戰鄭重建議】<br />\n#2 【晒你幾秒】唔好放過TVB，每日洗版任務 (樂信)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【國際文宣戰鄭重建議】</strong><br />\n依家連登仔喺國際文宣戰大大落後五毛，佢哋有組織大規模喺外媒FB、Twitter洗版，隨時扭轉輿論，如果你唔知發生乜事嘅，請睇：<br />\n<blockquote>【有圖請正視】求下大家唔好再輕敵！藍已經進化！你地睇下ifc!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahiAOrU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahiAOrU</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>參考抵制TVB嘅經驗</strong></span>，請有心打國際文宣嘅巴絲打做以下事情：<br />\n1. 喺連登搵有心有力嘅巴絲打成立core group，搵方法小心地交換聯絡方法<br />\n2. Core group 傾集體行動/ 洗版 嘅目標<br />\n3. 以每日1-3 個任務形式，定時叫連登仔幫拖 (一定要有傳送門、有template，大家都忙，要盡量方便) <br />\n4. 想參與任務嘅巴絲，一定要互like comment，推comment上熱門 (藍絲comment可以2000以上like...)<br />\n<br />\n其實以上方法，我估對家都用緊，並非甚麼秘密<br />\n大家想贏國際文宣戰，要了解香港人嘅習性：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">快、即食、Too Long Didn't Read<br />\n個個開post要人，結果度度都無人，所以要有人協調</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n協調國際文宣戰方面，抵制TVB團隊成員太忙搞唔到，請有心人當仁不讓、擔起大旗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9up完畢</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"643d20586ee9557cf2fc6d6a380d345d33473da6","tid":1573560,"uid":267969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TVB越來越唔掂，<br />\n推個「唱好香港」節目賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nkeep住個氣勢到年底啦！</span></span><br />\nTVB下個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約<br />\n廣告界多返強調，去FB洗版係有用ga</strong><br />\n<br />\n本身見幸福傷風素落咁多TVB廣告就決定罷食，轉食樂信。點知原來樂信都係落TVB廣告。下次寧願去問藥房佬配藥都唔食你。<br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.影張產品相，放上Facebook留言不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日精選@16 Sep 2019<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>樂信</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nestlebabyhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnestlebabyhk%2F&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=5ad88db5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nestlebabyhk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請用幾秒</span></strong>去派嬲、留言、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得?</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌只開行動post，順便follow埋<br />\n<br />\n<strong>※留言template，二擇其一，歡迎創意留言。</strong><br />\n1️⃣<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣<br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70208831_453263368863851_2970123013653004288_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQkEP4ilVK-1ZpsKfH41JjFcvRg_jDvZTpUBXlGt74MpkjRJQmqZkhw4KaKvAl0s-LQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=be28aa1128699baa948aab6f1957e50c&amp;oe=5DF3F2D3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70208831_453263368863851_2970123013653004288_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQkEP4ilVK-1ZpsKfH41JjFcvRg_jDvZTpUBXlGt74MpkjRJQmqZkhw4KaKvAl0s-LQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Dbe28aa1128699baa948aab6f1957e50c%26oe%3D5DF3F2D3&h=1fa9dc27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>更多: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span><br />\n消費前諗清楚<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=4eeae1a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=3d33846c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=794b6228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊綜合頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb%5B%2Fquote%5D&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=5763f6a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb[/quote]</a>"},{"pid":"5da5c895b1142ab3eb91716994fb6478fcb1a5d5","tid":1573560,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/so4yF19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u